      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted QoIs (hemolysis index) directly correspond to clinical acceptance criterion with demonstrated sensitivity analysis.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index is the correct QoI; sensitivity analysis performed but does not cover shear stress model parameter uncertainty, which is the dominant source of hemolysis prediction variability."
